{"tid":973381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"軟萌女偶像徵老公　下嫁條件「月給11萬」　特殊專長讓你錢全吐出來","createTime":"2019-01-08T06:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T06:57:07.000Z","uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d52734d1aad79afde624aea9c65df3c4efbf5261","tid":973381,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"文／厭世小羊<br />\n&nbsp;還記得小羊以前追星的時候，都會幻想自己有一天能成為某某歐巴的老婆，幻想終究是幻想，還是要回頭面對現實，但日本最近有位水汪汪大眼的軟萌女偶像，在自己的推特上PO文「徵求老公」，讓不少日本網友超興奮，因為這是能和自己最愛的偶像，緊密聯繫的大好機會！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3815/3815734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3815%2F3815734.jpg&h=b458b9a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自Twitter@HarupyonTen6）<br />\n這位女偶像是日本女團「TEN6」中的成員藍川はるか，元旦當天她突然拋出震撼彈，說只要能做到每個月給她40萬日幣的生活費（約台幣11萬左右）就能和她結婚，且婚後雙方分居各住在自己家裡都沒關係。<br />\n只要對她開的條件認同，在「TEN6」舉辦活動時，將寫好的結婚證書和薪資條、自我介紹等等，拿到物販處就OK了，有不少日本網友疑惑，為何她要這麼做？原來背後原因是與家人有關。<br />\n她提到因為家中的長輩有可能今年就會過世了，所以想讓他們看到自己幸福結婚的樣子，有網友就質疑藍川はるか根本就是在找ATM，偶像難道沒有賺錢嗎？還有網友問她「40萬日幣是給半年嗎？」，她回「是給一生！」，雖然生活費要價不斐，但因為是萌妹偶像，事後聽說有不少認真的日本男子手刀衝去報名！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3815/3815689.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3815%2F3815689.jpg&h=42ca599b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自Twitter@HarupyonTen6）<br />\n不過其實藍川はるか除了是偶像以外，還有另一個身份是「職業摔角手」，如果結了婚，哪天繳不出生活費給老婆，不知道下場會不會和下圖一樣，被老婆直接重擊打飛趕出家門。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3815/3815729.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3815%2F3815729.jpg&h=3826b83b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自Twitter@HarupyonTen6）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F40887&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=03e9afee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40887</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://rr.img.naver.jp/mig?src=http%3A%2F%2Fimgcc.naver.jp%2Fkaze%2Fmission%2FUSER%2F20170318%2F75%2F7436425%2F33%2F900x1200x48751dc8f5b03c1bb616342.jpg%2F300%2F600&amp;twidth=300&amp;theight=600&amp;qlt=80&amp;res_format=jpg&amp;op=r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frr.img.naver.jp%2Fmig%3Fsrc%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fimgcc.naver.jp%252Fkaze%252Fmission%252FUSER%252F20170318%252F75%252F7436425%252F33%252F900x1200x48751dc8f5b03c1bb616342.jpg%252F300%252F600%26twidth%3D300%26theight%3D600%26qlt%3D80%26res_format%3Djpg%26op%3Dr&h=55c8ab1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://fresh-club.info/photogallery/pictures/85493_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffresh-club.info%2Fphotogallery%2Fpictures%2F85493_s.jpg&h=5a6155a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3934a02d19bf9388e400d5d01abb61e1b3c05fb","tid":973381,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"職業摔角手都係做戲<br />\n連登仔個個好打過曹星如 怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">#曲線要講明</span></div>"},{"pid":"570f5849c4b582751f750ca7573f72fb36d0add3","tid":973381,"uid":30578,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T06:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3815/3815729.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3815%2F3815729.jpg&h=3826b83b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25712bd074e5d89b203ccffc8f25fafc61efabe0","tid":973381,"uid":90890,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T06:13:43.000Z","msg":"4皮一個月，我一日一千去叫雞都仲有成皮俾tips<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494